OSI - Open systems inerconnection : there are 7 layers in OSI

1 Application - Software (users)    
2 Presantation - Collects the data from application in a Binary format 
3 Session - authenticate / encription 
4 Transport - To control the data flow 
5 Network - to communicate with other users for {exmp router}Routing and IP addressing   
6 Data Link - Communication inside the same network
